05:44.977 --> 05:48.915
Well, you've looked horrible
longer, so I guess you win.

05:50.516 --> 05:51.718
Yeah.

05:54.687 --> 05:56.055
What do you want?

05:57.924 --> 06:00.493
You remember I had a son?

06:00.560 --> 06:01.594
Rafael.

06:03.529 --> 06:04.664
Yeah.

06:04.731 --> 06:08.768
That's him,
like, at five or six.

06:08.868 --> 06:11.371
Well, he's 13 now,
and I wanna
get him out of Mexico.

06:11.437 --> 06:13.239
I wanna get him up here.
I wanna do the right thing.

06:13.339 --> 06:15.007
I want him to live with me.

06:15.074 --> 06:17.877
What does his mother think
about that?

06:18.845 --> 06:22.014
Yeah, well, Leta,

06:22.081 --> 06:24.617
-she's a nutcase.
-Oh.

06:24.717 --> 06:27.754
I mean, she was fun
at a party, but...

06:28.888 --> 06:30.223
and she gave me him.

06:30.289 --> 06:32.592
Yeah.

06:32.692 --> 06:35.862
But he's in trouble.
Mike, the kid's in trouble.

06:35.928 --> 06:37.797
