06:43.236 --> 06:46.372
I have legal issues.
I can't go back into Mexico.

06:47.473 --> 06:49.242
He's being abused.

06:49.308 --> 06:50.943
How do you know that?

06:51.043 --> 06:52.612
Well, I don't know it
directly from him,

06:52.712 --> 06:53.813
if that's what
you're asking me,

06:53.913 --> 06:55.882
but I know that.

06:55.948 --> 06:57.617
I know it
from people around her,

06:57.717 --> 06:59.152
and she's a mess.

06:59.252 --> 07:01.554
And she's letting the kid
be abused.

07:01.621 --> 07:04.824
Uh... Well, I don't know
what you want from me

07:04.924 --> 07:06.959
'cause, you know...

07:07.059 --> 07:09.162
