18:22.101 --> 18:23.435
Two.

18:23.502 --> 18:24.937
Three.

18:25.003 --> 18:26.405
Four.

18:26.472 --> 18:28.607
-Give me my rooster!
-Five.

18:28.674 --> 18:31.410
